                <label.designator>5</label.designator>
                <footnote.body>
                    <para>
                        <bop/>
                        <bos/>
                        <paratext>The Panel&apos;s consideration of’ the number of cases as a factor in determining
                            whether to order transfer under <cite.query w-src-number="0304913945" w-seq-number="00008"
                                                                        w-ref-type="LQ" w-normalized-cite="28USCAS1407"
                                                                        w-pub-number="1000546"
                                                                        ID="I08d194a0680811e8865b9f61650dcdcd">28
                                U.S.C.A. § 1407
                            </cite.query> is discussed in <cite.query w-ref-type="NA" w-normalized-cite="MDLITMANs5:18"
                                                                      w-pub-number="185218"
                                                                      ID="I01d5e6f0680911e88f4a9c1f64101294">§
                                5:18</cite.query>.
